            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="https://s22908.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/0a918fde-35e2-4f93-96a4-1e7efa8efb4f.png"
                    alt="Service History" class="service-icon">
                <h4>View Service History</h4>
                <p>Access detailed service records for your car to make informed decisions.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn-primary">Learn More</a>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1282875224/vector/car-search-icon-for-web-and-apps.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=J0-G3Krk5tLAHsw-fUqXZthdhsuSwSQTABpJcioOMXo="
                    alt="Buy Car" class="service-icon">
                <h4>Buy a second hand Car </h4>
                <p>Explore a wide range of cars and find your dream car today.</p>
                <a href="http://localhost:8080/2ndhandcar" class="btn-primary">Browse Cars</a>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <img src="https://png.pngtree.com/png-vector/20220119/ourlarge/pngtree-gear-logo-picture-png-image_4225494.png"
                    alt="Accessories" class="service-icon">
                <h4>Car Accessories</h4>
                <p>Enhance your vehicle with the latest car accessories and upgrades.</p>
                <a href="http://localhost:8080/accessories" class="btn-primary">Shop Now</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>




    <!-- Reviews Section -->
    <section id="reviews" class="testimonial-section">
        <h3>What Our Customers Say</h3>
        <div class="testimonial-container">
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <p>"Great service, found my dream car in no time!"</p>
                <p class="customer-name">John Doe</p>
                <p class="car-model">Audi A4</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <p>"Amazing variety and competitive prices. Highly recommend!"</p>
                <p class="customer-name">Jane Smith</p>
                <p class="car-model">BMW 5 Series</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-card">
                <p>"The process was simple and efficient. Very satisfied!"</p>
                <p class="customer-name">Michael Lee</p>
                <p class="car-model">Mercedes E-Class</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section id="faq" class="faq-section">
        <h3>Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
        <div class="faq-item">
            <h4>How do I search for cars?</h4>
            <p>Use the search bar in the top navigation to enter car models or browse through the categories on the
                homepage to find cars that meet your preferences.</p>
